<p>Yes, it would appear that Donald Trump feels Kim Jong-un’s pain. It’s
 not easy to take over a regime at 27. Especially when you’re starving 
your own people to build a standing army of 1.3 million soldiers. Life 
sure seems hard at the top.</p>
<p class="">Trump may not want to be the president anymore, but he may be up for dictator of North Korea. </p>
